aa(lp16
VMy life is guided by two great passions,
p17
aVand the first is automobiles.
p18
aVI literally grew up with the Ford Motor Company.
p19
aVI thought it was so cool as a little boy
p20
aVwhen my dad would bring home the latest Ford or Lincoln
p21
aVand leave it in the driveway.
