aVAnd that's a belief that I share.
p65
aa(lp66
VMy other great passion is the environment.
p67
aVAnd as a young boy, I used to go up to Northern Michigan
p68
aVand fish in the rivers that Hemingway fished in
p69
aVand then later wrote about.
p70
aVAnd it really struck me
p71
aVas the years went by,
p72
aVin a very negative way,
p73
aVwhen I would go to some stream that I'd loved,
p74
aVand was used to walking through this field
p75
aVthat was once filled with fireflies,
p76
aVand now had a strip mall or a bunch of condos on it.
p77
aVAnd so even at a young age,
p78
aVthat really resonated with me,
p79
aVand the whole notion of environmental preservation,
p80
aVat a very basic level, sunk in with me.
p81
aa(lp82
VAs a high-schooler, I started to read
p83
aVauthors like Thoreau and Aldo Leopold
p84
aVand Edward Abbey,
p85
aVand I really began to develop
p86
aVa deeper appreciation of the natural world.
