aVIn fact, when I got back to Detroit,
p113
aVmy environmental leanings weren't exactly embraced
p114
aVby those in my own company,
p115
aVand certainly by those in the industry.
p116
aVI had some very interesting conversations,
p117
aVas you can imagine.
p118
aVThere were some within Ford
p119
aVwho believed that all this ecological nonsense
p120
aVshould just disappear
p121
aVand that I needed to stop hanging out
p122
aVwith "environmental wackos."
