p359
aa(lp360
VWe need our best and our brightest
p361
aVto start entertaining this issue.
p362
aVCompanies, entrepreneurs, venture capitalists,
p363
aVthey all need to understand
p364
aVthis is a huge business opportunity,
p365
aVas well as an enormous social problem.
p366
aVAnd just as these groups
p367
aVembrace the green energy challenge \u2014
p368
aVand it's really been amazing to me to watch
p369
aVhow much brain power, how much money
p370
aVand how much serious thought
p371
aVhas, really over the last three years,
p372
aVjust poured into the green energy field.
